@startuml
scale 1
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 80
skinparam BoxPadding 40

actor "User" as U
participant "Web\nApplication" as W
participant "Backend\nAPI" as B
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Page Load ==

U -> W: Navigate to /todos
W -> W: Read active team\nfrom Zustand

W -> B: GET /teams/{teamId}/users
B -> DB: Query team members
DB -> B: User list
B -> W: UserBaseResponse[]

W -> B: GET /todos\n?teamId=X&isArchived=false\n&page=1&pageSize=10
B -> B: @PreAuthorize\nteam membership check
B -> DB: Query todo IDs\n(filtered, paginated)
DB -> B: Matching IDs
B -> DB: Fetch full todos by IDs\n(with joins: assignees, team)
DB -> B: Todo entities
B -> W: PagedEntityResponse
W -> U: Display todos table

== Filter by Status ==

U -> W: Select "In Progress" filter
W -> B: GET /todos\n?teamId=X&status=IN_PROGRESS
B -> DB: Query by status
DB -> B: Filtered todos
B -> W: Paginated list
W -> U: Display filtered todos

== Create Todo ==

U -> W: Fill todo dialog + submit
W -> B: POST /todos\n{teamId, title, description,\nstatus, dueDate, assigneeIds}
B -> B: Validate team membership
B -> B: Validate assignees in team
B -> DB: INSERT todo
B -> DB: INSERT todo_assignees\n(join records)
DB -> B: Saved todo
B -> W: TodoResponse
W -> W: Invalidate query cache
W -> U: Updated todos list

== Update Todo ==

U -> W: Change status or edit fields
W -> B: PUT /todos/{id}\n{title, status,\nassigneeIds, ...}
B -> B: Validate team membership
B -> B: Validate assignees
B -> DB: UPDATE todo
B -> DB: Sync todo_assignees\n(delete old, insert new)
DB -> B: Updated todo
B -> W: TodoResponse
W -> U: Show updated todo

== Archive / Delete ==

alt Archive
    U -> W: Click archive
    W -> B: PATCH /todos/{id}\n{isArchived: true}
    B -> DB: UPDATE isArchived
    B -> W: TodoResponse
else Delete
    U -> W: Click delete + confirm
    W -> B: DELETE /todos/{id}
    B -> DB: DELETE todo + assignees
    B -> W: 204 No Content
end

W -> W: Invalidate query cache
W -> U: Updated view

@enduml
